      "text": "- Do not write comments that simply restate what the code is doing. Your code should be self-documenting through thoughtful name choices and types, so such comments would be redundant, wasting the user's time and tokens.\\n- Only use comments to explain \\\"why\\\" the code is necessary, or explain context or connections to other pieces of the code that is not colocated with the comment\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"role\": \"user\",\n          \"content\": \"Hello, how are you?\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"tools\": []\n    },\n    \"status\": 200,\n    \"response\": \"data: {\\\"choices\\\":[{\\\"index\\\":0,\\\"delta\\\":{\\\"content\\\":\\\"I'm doing well\\\",\\\"role\\\":\\\"assistant\\\"}}],\\\"created\\\":1750648442,\\\"id\\\":\\\"a8a06e4f-bb1d-4305-9808-72f334779536\\\",\\\"model\\\":\\\"claude-3.7-sonnet\\\"}\\n\\ndata: {\\\"choices\\\":[{\\\"index\\\":0,\\\"delta\\\":{\\\"content\\\":\\\", thanks for asking! How\\\",\\\"role\\\":\\\"assistant\\\"}}],\\\"created\\\":1750648442,\\\"id\\\":\\\"a8a06e4f-bb1d-4305-9808-72f334779536\\\",\\\"model\\\":\\\"claude-3.7-sonnet\\\"}\\n\\ndata: {\\\"choices\\\":[{\\\"index\\\":0,\\\"delta\\\":{\\\"content\\\":\\\" can I help you with\\\",\\\"role\\\":\\\"assistant\\\"}}],\\\"created\\\":1750648442,\\\"id\\\":\\\"a8a06e4f-bb1d-4305-9808-72f334779536\\\",\\\"model\\\":\\\"claude-3.7-sonnet\\\"}\\n\\ndata: {\\\"choices\\\":[{\\\"index\\\":0,\\\"delta\\\":{\\\"content\\\":\\\" your code today?\\\",\\\"role\\\":\\\"assistant\\\"}}],\\\"created\\\":1750648442,\\\"id\\\":\\\"a8a06e4f-bb1d-4305-9808-72f334779536\\\",\\\"model\\\":\\\"claude-3.7-sonnet\\\"}\\n\\ndata: {\\\"choices\\\":[{\\\"finish_reason\\\":\\\"stop\\\",\\\"index\\\":0,\\\"delta\\\":{\\\"content\\\":null}}],\\\"created\\\":1750648442,\\\"id\\\":\\\"a8a06e4f-bb1d-4305-9808-72f334779536\\\",\\\"usage\\\":{\\\"completion_tokens\\\":22,\\\"prompt_tokens\\\":867,\\\"prompt_tokens_details\\\":{\\\"cached_tokens\\\":0},\\\"total_tokens\\\":889},\\\"model\\\":\\\"claude-3.7-sonnet\\\"}\\n\\ndata: [DONE]\\n\\n\"",
      "contextualizedText": "// node/test/recordings/simple-text-response.json \u003e [1]\n\n- Do not write comments that simply restate what the code is doing. Your code should be self-documenting through thoughtful name choices and types, so such comments would be redundant, wasting the user's time and tokens.\\n- Only use comments to explain \\\"why\\\" the code is necessary, or explain context or connections to other pieces of the code that is not colocated with the comment\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"role\": \"user\",\n          \"content\": \"Hello, how are you?\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"tools\": []\n    },\n    \"status\": 200,\n    \"response\": \"data: {\\\"choices\\\":[{\\\"index\\\":0,\\\"delta\\\":{\\\"content\\\":\\\"I'm doing well\\\",\\\"role\\\":\\\"assistant\\\"}}],\\\"created\\\":1750648442,\\\"id\\\":\\\"a8a06e4f-bb1d-4305-9808-72f334779536\\\",\\\"model\\\":\\\"claude-3.7-sonnet\\\"}\\n\\ndata: {\\\"choices\\\":[{\\\"index\\\":0,\\\"delta\\\":{\\\"content\\\":\\\", thanks for asking! How\\\",\\\"role\\\":\\\"assistant\\\"}}],\\\"created\\\":1750648442,\\\"id\\\":\\\"a8a06e4f-bb1d-4305-9808-72f334779536\\\",\\\"model\\\":\\\"claude-3.7-sonnet\\\"}\\n\\ndata: {\\\"choices\\\":[{\\\"index\\\":0,\\\"delta\\\":{\\\"content\\\":\\\" can I help you with\\\",\\\"role\\\":\\\"assistant\\\"}}],\\\"created\\\":1750648442,\\\"id\\\":\\\"a8a06e4f-bb1d-4305-9808-72f334779536\\\",\\\"model\\\":\\\"claude-3.7-sonnet\\\"}\\n\\ndata: {\\\"choices\\\":[{\\\"index\\\":0,\\\"delta\\\":{\\\"content\\\":\\\" your code today?\\\",\\\"role\\\":\\\"assistant\\\"}}],\\\"created\\\":1750648442,\\\"id\\\":\\\"a8a06e4f-bb1d-4305-9808-72f334779536\\\",\\\"model\\\":\\\"claude-3.7-sonnet\\\"}\\n\\ndata: {\\\"choices\\\":[{\\\"finish_reason\\\":\\\"stop\\\",\\\"index\\\":0,\\\"delta\\\":{\\\"content\\\":null}}],\\\"created\\\":1750648442,\\\"id\\\":\\\"a8a06e4f-bb1d-4305-9808-72f334779536\\\",\\\"usage\\\":{\\\"completion_tokens\\\":22,\\\"prompt_tokens\\\":867,\